---
title: "_setFeeAggregator (BaseAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_live: _whenNoLiveAuctions()
    q_check_live --> q_revert_live: live auction exists
    q_revert_live --> [*]: revert LiveAuction
    q_check_live --> q_check_zero: no live auctions
    q_check_zero --> q_revert_zero: feeAggregator == address(0)
    q_revert_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroAddress
    q_check_zero --> q_check_same: feeAggregator != address(0)
    q_check_same --> q_revert_same: current == feeAggregator
    q_revert_same --> [*]: revert ValueNotUpdated
    q_check_same --> q_check_interface: current != feeAggregator
    q_check_interface --> q_revert_iface: feeAggregator != this and not supportsInterface
    q_revert_iface --> [*]: revert InvalidFeeAggregator
    q_check_interface --> q_update: feeAggregator == this or supportsInterface
    q_update --> [*]: s_feeAggregator = feeAggregator, emit FeeAggregatorSet

    note right of q_check_interface
        INV-001: feeAggregator must implement IFeeAggregator unless it is self
        INV-002: No configuration changes during live auctions
    end note
